description:

Today she meets Yasmine Loven. A voluptuous carmel chocolate babe with amazing breasts. Yasmine has natural talent and has been picking up her game each time she hits our mats but her matches are hit or miss. Some days she on and some days she’s just not. She’s coming off a loss in an unimpressive match with Penny Barber where she was creamed badly in the welter weight tournament. Depending on if the Yasmine who is “on” shows up today, this could be a brutal awakening for Lyla Storm. But if the mediocre Yasmine shows up today, Lyla could be slinging that cock deep in the black hole. These girls battle to the bitter end. Up to the buzzer in round 3 they both fight their hearts out. Today we find out if Big tits win over Legs!
